born three months premature,

00:19:12.000 --> 00:19:15.500
must cope with the world
before her brain is ready.

00:19:17.130 --> 00:19:19.030
For more than two decades,

00:19:19.030 --> 00:19:21.360
developmental psychologist
Heidelise Als

00:19:21.360 --> 00:19:23.800
has been studying premies
like Elizabeth

00:19:23.800 --> 00:19:26.200
to learn
how their fragile brains,

00:19:26.200 --> 00:19:29.530
