darkness of the womb,

00:19:29.530 --> 00:19:32.030
adapt to the dazzle and buzz
of the world.

00:19:33.800 --> 00:19:37.600
ALS:
How does the difference
of inputs,

00:19:37.600 --> 00:19:43.230
of sound, of light, shape,
how the brain grows itself?

