00:21:22.200 --> 00:21:24.700
And now miracles
are becoming more common.

00:21:24.700 --> 00:21:27.130
In fact, it's more or less
an expectation

00:21:27.130 --> 00:21:29.160
that a premature infant
will live.

00:21:29.160 --> 00:21:32.130
Then we've discovered
that that may not be enough.

00:21:32.130 --> 00:21:35.100
We've got to go a step further
and ask ourselves,

00:21:35.100 --> 00:21:40.630
"Despite our very best efforts
medically, they aren't...

00:21:40.630 --> 00:21:43.530
quite comparable
