at Children's Hospital
in Boston.

00:31:55.730 --> 00:31:58.000
Does the brain's
remarkable plasticity

00:31:58.000 --> 00:32:01.200
make preemies like Elizabeth
especially vulnerable?

00:32:05.100 --> 00:32:08.400
Does an intensive care unit
that mimics the womb

00:32:08.400 --> 00:32:11.160
have a demonstrable effect
on the brain?

